    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>Louis Vuitton to Open Store at The Westchester</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <byline class="print_byline">By Merri Rosenberg</byline>
      <byline class="normalized_byline">Rosenberg, Merri</byline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Louis Vuitton plans to open store at The Westchester mall in White Plains, NY (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Louis Vuitton will open a store next month in The Westchester in White Plains, selling the kind of luxury goods that are usually found on Madison Avenue. At the 1,700-square-foot store, fans of the brand's prints and patterns will find handbags, small leather goods and accessories like scarves.</p>
        <p>Louis Vuitton, a Paris-based subsidiary of the luxury goods conglomerate, LVMH, has been selling leather products since 1854 and has branches in about 20 malls.</p>
        <p>Merri Rosenberg</p>
      </block>
